{"word":"κλαίω","slug":"κλαίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰλαίω</el></b> [Albanian <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>] ‘express grief or sorrow aloud’ (not a silent dropping of tears or weeping such as ordinarily denoted by <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δακρύω\">δακρύω</a></el>)<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <b>cry, sob <a href='B:470 26:75'>Mt 26:75</a>; <a href='B:480 5:38'>Mk 5:38</a>; <a href='B:480 14:72'>14:72</a></b> (<el>ἐπιβαλὼν ἔϰλαιεν</el> he sobbed violently); <b><a href='B:490 7:13'>Lk 7:13</a>, <a href='B:490 7:32'>32</a>; <a href='B:490 8:52'>8:52</a>; <a href='B:490 19:41'>19:41</a>; <a href='B:500 11:31'>J 11:31</a>; <a href='B:500 20:13'>20:13</a>; <a href='B:510 9:39'>Ac 9:39</a>; <a href='B:520 12:15'>Ro 12:15</a>; <a href='B:530 7:30'>1 Cor 7:30</a>; <a href='B:660 5:1'>Js 5:1</a>; <a href='B:730 5:4'>Rv 5:4</a>; <a href='B:730 18:9'>18:9</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> <b>cry (over/for) <a href='B:470 2:18'>Mt 2:18</a>; <a href='B:730 18:9'>Rv 18:9</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κλάδος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κλάσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}